mods.abstract: Two color half sheet (blue and red on white) announcing Dick Clark's Caravan of Stars featuring the Byrds, We Five, Bo Diddley, Paul Revere and the Raiders, and the Duchess at the Municipal Auditorium on November 7. Poster features metal photoplates of the performers.
